<i>noun</i>: 호기 [호기], 콧대 [코때/콛때], 오만 [오ː만], 오기 [오ː기], 불손 [불쏜], 교만 [교만], 고자세 [고자세], 건방 [건방], 거만 [거ː만] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>호기 [호기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gallantry; intrepidity</dd><br>
<dd>씩씩하고 큰 기상.</dd><br>
<dd>A gallant and brave spirit.</dd><br>
<dd>2. arrogance; pomposity</dd><br>
<dd>거만한 태도로 잘난 척하는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude of putting on airs and behaving arrogantly.</dd><br>
<dt>콧대 [코때/콛때]</dt><br>
<dd>1. nose ridge</dd><br>
<dd>콧등의 높이 솟아 있는 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>The protruded part of the nose.</dd><br>
<dd>2. arrogance; pride</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 뽐내거나 거만한 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A showy or arrogant attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>오만 [오ː만]</dt><br>
<dd>arrogance; pride</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하고 건방짐. 또는 그런 태도나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being prideful and haughty, or such an attitude or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>오기 [오ː기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. being obstinate; being headstrong; being unyielding</dd><br>
<dd>능력은 부족하면서 지기 싫어하는 고집스러운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude of being stubborn, not given to losing despite one's lack of ability.</dd><br>
<dd>2. arrogance; putting on airs</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하고 건방지며 무례한 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of showing off, acting arrogantly, and being impolite.</dd><br>
<dt>불손 [불쏜]</dt><br>
<dd>insolence; arrogance</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 예의가 없거나 겸손하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>One's remarks or behavior being impolite or haughty.</dd><br>
<dt>교만 [교만]</dt><br>
<dd>arrogance; vanity</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하면서 남을 무시하고 말이나 행동이 건방짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of ignoring others while showing off and speaking or acting arrogantly.</dd><br>
<dt>고자세 [고자세]</dt><br>
<dd>rudeness; arrogance</dd><br>
<dd>상대방에게 거만하게 구는 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>An arrogant attitude toward others.</dd><br>
<dt>건방 [건방]</dt><br>
<dd>arrogance; impertinence; sauciness</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 주제를 모르고 지나치게 잘난 척하는 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude where someone is too proud of himself/herself, not realizing his/her real position.</dd><br>
<dt>거만 [거ː만]</dt><br>
<dd>arrogance; haughtiness</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하며 자기보다 남을 낮추어 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>A superior attitude in which a person looks down on others.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>